This paper deals with the problem of class imbalance in machine learning, which is a common issue in several sub-fields of computer science. The proposed algorithm involves clustering and boosting, which are techniques used in several areas of computer science such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data mining (cs.DM), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
